    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Term refers to the process of demagnetization, originally used in the context of warships, now extended to magnetic media such as audio tapes and computer storage media.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
